    "description": "<p>When you Critically Succeed or Fail on a  <strong>Spell Attack</strong> or a <strong>Spell</strong> <strong>Check</strong>, roll on the <strong>@UUID[Compendium.dc20rpg.roll-tables.RollTable.HxkcpDT6pEOIfYUk]{Wild Magic Table}</strong>.</p><p>If it’s a Critical Success you roll with ADV, if it’s a Critical Failure you roll with DisADV.</p><p>The effect lasts until the end of your next turn, unless otherwise stated. When yo<span data-token-index=\"1\" class=\"notion-enable-hover\">u roll on the Wild Magic Table in this way, yo</span>u gain ADV on the next <strong>Spell</strong> <strong>Check</strong> you make before the end of your n<span data-token-index=\"3\" class=\"notion-enable-hover\">ext turn.</span></p>",
